pinax-satchmo-buildout

This project aims to kick start websites using pinax and satchmo, providing the core buildout.cfg and settings files to get new projects up and running.

Requirements
 * git
 * mercurial
 * svn

Creating a website

 * add create-site.sh to your path
 * mkdir newproject;cd newproject
 * create-site.sh
 * edit settings.py and set database details
 * bin/django syncdb
 * bin/django build_media
 * bin/django 

Customizing settings

The default settings will use a full pinax install based off the social_project
You'll need to change the database details 

